data.description: Welcome home to 970 Welch Street in Golden, Colorado. This cozy bungalow provides a harmonious blend of comfort and charm. The heart of the home lies in the kitchen, where a new stainless steel high-efficiency LG refrigerator stands as a testament to both style and functionality. Meanwhile, the Goodman high-efficiency furnace and air conditioner installed in 2022 ensure comfort throughout the seasons. Recessed lighting illuminates the space with a gentle glow, enhancing the atmosphere of relaxation and warmth. Enjoy the convenience of minimal steps and brand new windows in the bedroom and living room, providing abundant natural light. All other double pane windows were installed in 2020. In the backyard, step onto the newly installed stamped concrete patio, surrounded by lush shade trees, inviting you to explore every corner of this delightful abode. Feel secure and at ease with new security lighting adorning both the front and back of the property, while fresh fencing installed in 2022 offers privacy and peace of mind. And when it's time to venture out, you're just moments away from Colorado Mills Mall, Union Square, Colfax Avenue, and 6th Avenue, offering a plethora of dining, shopping, and entertainment options.For nature enthusiasts, the picturesque Daniel's Park awaits just a block away, providing the perfect backdrop for outdoor adventures. Clean, well-loved, and exuding a sense of coziness, 970 Welch Street invites you to experience the best of Golden living in a home that feels like a sanctuary.
